%20from%20scratch'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20in%20a%20meeting%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673c9029ede4eeae39285527%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20he%20has%20not%20put%20in%20a%20bid%20for%20TikTok.%3Cp%3EAllison%20Robbert%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20says%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20acquire%20TikTok%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20law%20passed%20last%20year%20requires%20TikTok%20to%20sell%20to%20a%20US%20company%20or%20face%20a%20ban%20from%20app%20stores.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETikTok%20still%20faces%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20even%20after%20Trump's%2075-day%20extension.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20he%20does%20not%20plan%20to%20be%20TikTok's%20savior%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20actually%20put%20in%20a%20bid%20for%20TikTok%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20plans%20for%20what%20would%20I%20do%20if%20I%20had%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20during%20a%20virtual%20appearance%20at%20a%20recent%20business%20conference%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20signed%20a%20law%20last%20year%20that%20requires%20ByteDance%2C%20the%20Chinese%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-creators-what-to-do-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20divest%20from%20the%20popular%20social%20media%20app%20or%20face%20a%20ban%20from%20US%20app%20stores.%20The%20US%20government%20worries%20TikTok's%20Chinese%20ownership%20presents%20a%20security%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%20law%20in%20January%20before%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20giving%20ByteDance%20another%2075%20days%20to%20find%20a%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20investors%20have%20expressed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultra-wealthy-investors-want-buy-tiktok-plans-for-app-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest%20in%20purchasing%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20mogul%20Kevin%20O'Leary%20and%20former%20Dodgers%20owner%20Frank%20McCourt.%20Some%20have%20also%20wondered%20if%20Musk%2C%20who%20bought%20Twitter%20in%202022%20and%20rebranded%20it%20X%2C%20might%20also%20throw%20up%20his%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20first%20public%20comments%20on%20the%20matter%20came%20via%20video%20call%20at%20the%20WELT%20Economic%20Summit%20in%20Berlin%2C%20a%20gathering%20of%20politicians%20and%20CEOs%20hosted%20by%20Axel%20Springer%2C%20on%20January%2028.%20Axel%20Springer%20is%20Business%20Insider's%20parent%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20told%20the%20summit's%20guests%20he%20does%20not%20personally%20use%20TikTok%20and%20that%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20chomping%20at%20the%20bit%26quot%3B%20to%20acquire%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20acquisition%20of%20Twitter%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Brare%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20unusual%26quot%3B%20purchase.%20He%20said%20the%20acquisition%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bquite%20painful%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20he%20bought%20the%20company%20because%20he%20thought%20it%20was%20important%20to%20%26quot%3Bpreserve%20freedom%20of%20speech%20in%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20usually%20build%20companies%20from%20scratch%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20TikTok%20argued%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20banning%20the%20app%20in%20the%20United%20States%20would%20infringe%20on%20its%20users'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-upheld-supreme-court-ruling-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eright%20to%20free%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20however%2C%20said%20he%20only%20sees%20monetary%20reasons%20to%20buy%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20the%20same%20logic%20applies%20to%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20He%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20reasons%20he%20purchased%20Twitter.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20acquire%20things%20just%20for%20economic%20reasons.%20So%20it's%20not%20clear%20to%20me%20what%20the%20purpose%20of%20acquiring%20TikTok%20would%20be%20apart%20from%20economics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EByteDance%20has%20said%20it%20does%20not%20plan%20to%20sell%20TikTok%2C%20which%20means%20that%20if%20Trump%20does%20not%20intervene%2C%20TikTok%20could%20go%20dark%20in%20the%20United%20States%20by%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tiktok-purchase-twitter-x-social-media-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739046769000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a7b491eb4be2fff9a40bd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tiktok-purchase-twitter-x-social-media-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TikTok's%20Chinese%20owner%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20must%20find%20a%20buyer%20for%20the%20app%20or%20face%20a%20ban%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20make%20a%20bid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1098%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tiktok-purchase-twitter-x-social-media-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Unspoken%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Genealogy%20of%20Violence%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Aferrado%E2%80%99%20Take%20Top%20Honors%20at%20Clermont-