nsider.com%2Fteaching-my-son-to-do-chores-independently-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20pile%20of%20Lincoln%20Logs%20that%20would%20only%20appear%20back%20on%20the%20floor%20again%20repeatedly%20wasn't%20worth%20it%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20incorporated%20children's%20books%20and%20toys%20into%20our%20living%20space%20ever%20since%20our%20eldest%20child%20was%20born%2C%20and%20now%20that%20they%20are%203%20and%205%2C%20the%20chaos%20remains.%20Now%20it's%20just%20a%20mixture%20of%20Legos%20and%20play%20food%20instead%20of%20stacking%20cups%20and%20play%20mats.%20Our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecor-interior-decorator-adding-to-home-upgrades-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecorating%20aesthetic%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20easily%20be%20described%20as%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20kids.%26quot%3B%20I%20don't%20regret%20living%20this%20way%2C%20after%20all%2C%20my%20kids%20always%20have%20something%20to%20do%20at%20their%20fingertips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8a10352-993c-4913-9c84-29fc1ed21395%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20embrace%20fun%20and%20vibrancy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sometimes%20jealous%20of%20the%20families%20who%20own%20toys%20that%20perfectly%20match%20their%20furniture%20or%20who%20keep%20out%20only%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-of-organized-playrooms-cleaning-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%20toy%20bin%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20color%20sorted%20toys%2C%20but%20I%20know%20that's%20not%20for%20us.%20We've%20chosen%20to%20embrace%20the%20fun%20and%20vibrancy%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20toys%20and%20stuffed%20animals.%20In%20our%20house%2C%20there%20is%20always%20an%20assortment%20of%20activities%2C%20books%2C%20and%20toys%20in%20the%20living%20room%20and%20crafts%20happening%20at%20the%20kitchen%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20families%20have%20separate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-has-designed-over-1000-playrooms-shares-her-tips-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplayrooms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20toys%20always%20wind%20up%20strewn%20about%20and%20mixed%2C%20and%20someone%20has%20to%20clean%20it%20up%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%20We%20simply%20keep%20everything%20in%20our%20shared%20space%20so%20we%20have%20easy%20access%20to%20it%20and%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20bounce%20house%20is%20currently%20set%20up%20in%20our%20dining%20room.%20My%20husband%20occasionally%20works%20from%20home%2C%20out%20of%20his%20basement%20office%2C%20and%20having%20the%20bounce%20house%20on%20the%20main%20level%20makes%20it%20accessible%20even%20if%20he's%20working.%20And%20no%2C%20since%20they're%20using%20it%20frequently%2C%20I%20don't%20routinely%20roll%20it%20up%20into%20the%20storage%20bag%2C%20unless%20we're%20doing%20toy%20rotation%20or%20having%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20children%20help%20clean%20up%2C%20it%20will%20never%20be%20a%20perfectly%20clean%20visual.%20The%20families%20with%20pristinely%20organized%20toys%3F%20Let's%20be%20honest%2C%20an%20adult%20probably%20picked%20them%20up%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20using%20all%20of%20my%20free%20time%20on%20the%20futile%20attempt%20to%20make%20my%20house%20look%20child-free.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223708%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20green%20and%20blue%20inflatable%20bounce%20house%2C%20covered%20in%20stuffed%20animals%2C%20is%20set%20up%20inside%20a%20dining%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a61b5e7bb3f854015c253e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222781%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHaving%20the%20bounce%20house%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20of%20our%20house%2C%20instead%20of%20in%20the%20basement%2C%20means%20my%20husband%20can%20work%20from%20home%20without%20interruption.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anne%20James%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220b96f2b2-2172-4f40-be4b-c2e9e590b68b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20think%20upscale%20children's%20organization%20systems%20are%20worth%20the%20cost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20it%20looks%20beautifully%20curated%20when%20someone%20has%20matching%20baskets%20or%20play%20furniture%20that%20coordinates%20with%20their%20own%20decor.%20But%20I'm%20not%20buying%20expensive%20storage%20for%20our%20house.%20I%20wanted%20a%20cute%20storage%20tower%20for%20the%20small%20space%20next%20to%20our%20play%20kitchen%2C%20but%20at%20%2480%2C%20I%20passed.%20Instead%2C%20we're%20using%20a%20fabric%20storage%20bin%20to%20store%20the%20play%20food%20and%20accessories.%20I'd%20rather%20make%20a%20couple%20trips%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-visited-space-club-nyc-brooklyn-indoor-playground-expensive-fun-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekids%20play%20gym%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20go%20to%20a%20fun%20event%20instead%20of%20buying%20the%20more%20expensive%20storage%20tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f70e3737-f0e8-4e40-94c2-b7e3230037e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20kids%20help%20decorate%20our%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%20painted%20ceramics%2C%20sun%20catchers%2C%20ornaments%2C%20and%20more%20have%20found%20homes%20on%20our%20walls.%20We%20also%20encourage%20them%20to%20help%20us%20decorate%20for%20the%20holidays.%20For%20Memorial%20Day%2C%20my%20son%20was%20thrilled%20to%20stick%20patriotic%20pinwheels%20randomly%20throughout%20our%20lawn.%20For%20Christmas%2C%20we%20have%20small%20trees%20in%20each%20of%20the%20kids'%20rooms%2C%20and%20inevitably%20the%20ornaments%20wind%20up%20goofily%20(but%20lovingly)%20spread%20throughout%20the%20branches.%20And%20sometimes%20they%20%26quot%3Bdecorate%26quot%3B%20the%20floor%20by%20spilling%20flour%20when%20we're%20baking%20and%20play%20%26quot%3Bice%20skating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20embracing%20the%20chaos%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-of-thre-had-a-hard-time-decluttering-kids-stuff-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisorganization%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I'm%20encouraging%20their%20creativity%20and%20giving%20them%20space%20to%20explore%20the%20world%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec460b7c-a2e5-49f8-bde7-aa14fd8bf354%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEntertaining%20involves%20more%20prep%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20still%20entertain%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20more%20thought%20out%2C%20and%20I%20adjust%20the%20level%20of%20cleaning%20we%20do%20to%20the%20event.%20I%20tidy%20more%20before%20parties%20or%20for%20friends%20who%20have%20spotless%20houses%3B%20I'll%20clean%20less%20for%20a%20play%20date%20(unless%20it%20involves%20extra%20baby%20proofing).%20We%20entertain%20about%20the%20same%20amount%20as%20before%20kids%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20prep%20work%20beforehand.%20I%20tend%20to%20put%20away%20things%20we%20keep%20out%20day-to-day%2C%20such%20as%20the%20splat%20mat%20(a%20waterproof%2C%20washable%20floor%20mat%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20much%20easier%20than%20treating%20carpet%20stains)%20and%20panini%20maker%20(for%20almost%20daily%20quesadillas)%2C%20but%20the%20plastic%20picnic%20table%2C%20toy%20box%2C%20play%20kitchen%2C%20and%20similar%20items%20remain%20as%20part%20of%20our%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223692%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20living%20room%20cluttered%20with%20children's%20toys%20is%20shown.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a61c78bfebcc4d029e2c7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222769%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20living%20room%20is%20filled%20with%20toys%20and%20activities%20for%20the%20kids%2C%20which%20keeps%20us%20all%20together%20as%20a%20family.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anne%20James%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228680db8f-9937-421d-a6b2-dae50eb121ed%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20embracing%20the%20stage%20