%20Urban%20Naxal%20politics.%20Their%20politics%20is%20focussed%20on%20bringing%20anarchy%20and%20AAP-da%20was%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20same%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%2C%20he%20added%2C%20can%20now%20look%20forward%2C%20having%20rejected%20the%20politics%20of%20%26quot%3Bcorruption%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bidiocy%26quot%3B%20--%26quot%3BIt%20is%20my%20guarantee%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20-%20Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikaas%20and%20puri%20Dilli%20ka%20Vikaas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20left%20a%20clear%20footprint%20in%20neighbouring%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20recently%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%20opted%20for%20the%20party%20with%20good%20reason%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20law-and-order%20situation%20in%20neighbouring%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20once%20caused%20problems%2C%20but%20we%20worked%20to%20fix%20it.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20farmers%20suffered%20from%20drought%2C%20so%20we%20created%20Jalyukt%20Shivir%20to%20help%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20two%20NCR%20states%20-%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20already%20under%20the%20BJP%20belt%2C%20he%20said%20the%20victory%20in%20Delhi%20will%20help%20ensure%20better%20governance%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20double%20engine%20government%20will%20now%20ensure%20that%20all%20the%20party's%20election%20promises%20are%20kept.%20This%20would%20include%20clearing%20up%20the%20city%2C%20tackling%20pollution%2C%20garbage%20and%20sewage%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20this%2C%20he%20promised%20that%20the%20Yamuna%20river%20-%20which%20was%20catapulted%20into%20becoming%20an%20election%20issue%20after%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20allegation%20that%20Haryana%20is%20poisoning%20its%20waters%20-%20will%20become%20the%20%26quot%3Bidentity%20(pehchaan)%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promises%20made%20to%20women%20will%20also%20be%20kept%2C%