%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-to-fall-asleep-fast%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efall%20asleep%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Luckily%2C%20my%20third%20son%2C%20Ford%2C%20is%20only%20bored%20enough%20by%20his%20first%20name%20to%20swap%20it%20with%20his%20second%20(Grayson).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20they%20don't%20know%20is%20the%20immense%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20thought%2C%20obsession%2C%20consideration%2C%20and%20research%20that%20went%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpicked-son-baby-name-unique-no-longer-trendy-angry-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echoosing%20baby%20names%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20when%20it%20so%20clearly%20misses%20the%20mark%20in%20their%20minds%2C%20I%20can't%20help%20but%20get%20a%20bit%20sad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b64d22e-602b-4ddf-a68a-326afa24bc0c%5C%22%3EI%20was%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20to%20find%20the%20perfect%20names%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20grievances%20have%20led%20me%20to%20reexamine%20the%20naming%20process.%20When%20my%20kids%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BMom%2C%20why%20did%20you%20pick%20such%20a%20weird%20name%3F%26quot%3B%20I'm%20forced%20to%20think%20back%20to%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-full-time-not-worth-it-wouldnt-do-again-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enine%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20pondering%20and%20worrying%20about%20choosing%20just%20the%20right%20name.%20I%20took%20a%20lot%20into%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraham%20was%20named%20after%20his%20dad's%20middle%20name.%20James%20was%20named%20after%20a%20relative%2C%20while%20his%20middle%20name%2C%20John%2C%20was%20for%20my%20grandfather%2C%20who%20got%20to%20meet%20him%20for%20a%20few%20short%20months%20before%20passing.%20And%20then%2C%20there%20was%20Ford%20%E2%80%94%20after%20two%20days%20of%20birthing%2C%20it%20just%20seemed%20like%20a%20fun%20random%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20kids%20don't%20care%20about%20legacy%20or%20family%20names%2C%20so%20they%20insist%20on%20changing%20their%20name%20to%20that%20of%20their%20favorite%20NFL%20player%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamarr-chase-tee-higgins-bengals-contracts-free-agency-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJa'Maar%20Chase%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20felt%20obligated%20to%20pick%20a%20name%20that%20screams%20leadership%20in%20the%20boardroom%20but%20fits%20them%20at%20each%20stage%20%E2%80%94%20from%20cute%20squishy%20babyhood%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Ffirst-date-ideas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20date%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20wise%20old%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20had%20to%20ensure%20the%20names%20were%20common%20enough%20that%20they%20wouldn't%20be%20too%20unusual%20but%20not%20so%20common%20that%20they%20just%20blended%20in%20with%20the%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20my%20kids%20understood%20all%20that%20pressure%20I%20was%20under.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bd6e15a-27c1-4f63-9ba9-8016647c75c6%5C%22%3EI%20remind%20myself%20that%20their%20complaints%20are%20not%20personal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20kids%20see%20a%20YouTuber%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bsweet%26quot%3B%20name%20and%20a%20sweet%20life%20to%20go%20with%20it%2C%20they%20revert%20to%20their%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-youngest-13-eldest-26-i-raised-them-differently-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyounger%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20been%20pretty%20emotional%20about%20it.%20After%20all%2C%20I%20considered%20so%20many%20things%20to%20help%20pick%20the%20perfect%20name%20for%20them%20without%20knowing%20them%20yet%20%E2%80%94%20an%20impossible%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20more%20experienced%20parent%2C%20bracing%20for%20my%20fourth%20and%20fifth%20kids%20to%20come%20at%20me%20with%20the%20same%20vengeanc