wo-road-assets-at-enterprise-value-of-rs-4-184-cr-125020801330_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20the%20assets%20are%20annuity-based%20and%20located%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcube-highways-invit-buys-two-road-assets-at-enterprise-value-of-rs-4-184-cr-125020801330_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Delhi%20Debacle%3A%20Can%20Kejriwal%20Ever%20Recover%20From%20This%20Wipeout%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMany%20may%20be%20tempted%20to%20write%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20obituary%20today%2C%20but%20that%20may%20be%20both%20hasty%20and%20tragic.%20The%20AAP's%20defeat%20in%20Delhi%20is%20basically%20a%20journey%20from%20Dreamland%20to%20Crashland.%20Much%20before%20the%20results%20were%20out%2C%20I%20had%20argued%20that%20this%20was%20the%20most%20opportune%20time%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20win%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20elections%20are%20shocking%20for%20both%20AAP%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20but%20it's%20they%20who%20must%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20rout%2C%20and%20gracefully%20accept%20their%20mistakes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20had%20emerged%20on%20the%20national%20scene%20as%20a%20radical%20revolutionary%20who%20promised%20to%20change%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20country.%20Instead%2C%20it%20was%20politics%20that%20changed%20Kejriwal.%20Twelve%20years%20in%20power%20turned%20him%20into%20yet%20another%20politician%20who%20lost%20all%20his%20moral%20lustre%20and%20charisma.%20Nothing%20could%20be%20more%20tragic%20than%20the%20defeat%20of%20Kejriwal%20from%20his%20own%20seat%2C%20the%20New%20Delhi%20constituency.%20It's%20a%20lesson%20for%20all%20politicians%20who%20think%20they%20are%20bigger%20than%20the%20party%20and%20the%20collective%20wisdom%20of%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20things%20went%20against%20the%20AAP%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Same%20Old%2C%20Same%20Old%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20AAP's%20biggest%20undoing%20was%20that%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20seen%20as%20a%20party%20with%20a%20difference.%20Moral%20capital%20used%20to%20be%20its%20unique%20asset%2C%20something%20that%20few%20parties%20in%20contemporary%20politics%20could%20claim.%20But%20over%20time%2C%20the%20AAP%20sacrificed%20its%20core%20values%3B%20it%20became%20vulnerable%20as%20its%20most%20loyal%20supporters%20lost%20confidence%20in%20both%20the%20party%20and%20its%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20thing%20had%20happened%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%201984%2C%20when%20it%20could%20win%20only%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20election.%20Yes%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20party's%20dismal%20performance%2C%20but%20it%20was%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20abandoned%20its%20core%20ideological%20Hindutva%20pitch%20and%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20be%20secular.%20True%2C%20the%20AAP%20is%20not%20an%20ideological%20party%2C%20but%20it%20had%20a%20certain%20moral%20virtue%20and%20responsibility.%20It%20was%20this%20moral%20image%20that%20had%20helped%20it%20win%20landslide%20mandates%20in%20both%202015%20and%202020%20assembly%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Losing%20The%20Moral%20Edge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20serious%20corruption%20charges%20dented%20Kejriwal's%20image.%20The%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20proved%20to%20be%20an%20albatross%20around%20his%20neck.%20It%20landed%20him%20in%20jail%2C%20along%20with%20his%20colleagues%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20others.%20And%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Sheesh%20Mahal'%20controversy%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20final%20straw.%20Voters%20could%20not%20believe%20that%20a%20leader%20who%20criticised%20every%20politician%20for%20their%20wealth%20and%20fancy%20bungalows%20had%20ironically%20built%20a%20plush%20house%20worth%20crores%20for%20himself.%20The%20leaked%20images%20of%20his%20renovated%20home%20did%20more%20damage%20to%20Kejriwal's%20personal%20image%20than%20the%20liquor%20scam.%20He%20did%20realise%20this%2C%20and%20attempted%20some%20damage%20control%20by%20resigning%20from%20office%20and%20leaving%20the%20chief%20minister's%20bungalow%20for%20a%20much%20more%20modest%20accommodation.%20But%20the%20deed%20was%20done.%20The%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20had%20been%20the%20biggest%20pillar%20of%20the%20AAP's%20success%20story%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20had%20already%20been%20disillusioned%2C%20and%20ended%20up%20deserting%20the%20AAP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20The%20Policy%20Paralysis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20the%20non-performance%20of%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20its%20third%20term%20from%202020%20to%202025%20contributed%20to%20its%20rout.%20In%20its%20first%20full%20term%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20delivering%20on%20its%20promises.%20Other%20than%20the%20provision%20of%20free%20electricity%20and%20water%2C%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20were%20turned%20into%20better%20centres%20for%20education%2C%20a%20step%20that%20brought%20global%20appreciation%20for%20the%20government.%20The%20introduction%20of%20Mohalla%20clinics%20was%20also%20an%20excellent%20step%20to%20improve%20primary%20healthcare.%20It%20became%20a%20hit%20among%20large%20sections%20of%20society%20that%20could%20not%20afford%20costly%20medical%20care%20at%20private%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20term%2C%20however%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20suffered%20from%20policy%20and%20administrative%20paralysis.%20It%20was%20seen%20as%20constantly%20wrangling%20with%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20for%20power.%20The%20tussle%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20AAP%20government%20brought%20governance%20in%20the%20city%20to%20a%20standstill.%20Broken%20roads%20and%20open%20sewer%20lines%20were%20for%20everyone%20to%20see.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3E4.%20When%20Theatrics%20Don't%20Pay%20Off%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourthly%2C%2010%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time%20for%20anti-incumbency%20to%20set%20in%20against%20any%20government.%20Even%20the%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20could%20not%20avoid%20the%20repercussions%20of%20anti-incumbency%20in%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20elections.%20Despite%20the%20party's%20expectations%20that%20it%20would%20get%20more%20than%20400%20seats%20along%20with%20its%20allies%2C%20it%20could%20not%20get%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20smaller%20allies%20to%20form%20a%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20was%20no%20exception.%20Its%20misstep%20was%20that%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20arrest%20and%20address%20the%20disillusionment%20of%20its%20voters%2C%20it%20indulged%20in%20theatrics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Volunteers%20Were%20Tired%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20AAP%20failed%20to%20strengthen%20its%20biggest%20asset%3A%20its%20selfless%20volunteer%20force.%20It%20couldn't%20create%20a%20party%20structure%20across%20the%20national%20capital.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20always%20had%20the%20advantage%20of%20having%20a%20robust%20organisation.%20Kejriwal%2C%20by%20nature%2C%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20that.%20Slowly%20and%20steadily%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20many%20volunteers%2C%20feeling%20ignored%2C%20exploited%2C%20disheartened%20and%20disillusioned%2C%20either%20left%20the%20AAP%20and%20went%20back%20to%20their%20usual%20lives%2C%20or%2C%20they%20joined%20other%20parties.%20In%20this%20election%2C%20the%20AAP%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20paid%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20it%20might%20be%20too%20early%20to%20be%20writing%20an%20obituary%20for%20the%20AAP.%20The%20party%20has%20lost%20almost%2010%25%20votes%20compared%20to%20its%20tally%20in%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections.%20But%20it%20still%20commands%20almost%2043%25%20votes.%20It%20still%20controls%20the%20capital's%20municipal%20body.%20In%20Punjab%2C%20it%20has%20a%20government%20with%20more%20than%2090%20MLAs%2C%20and%20has%20also%20made%20its%20presence%20felt%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Goa.%20And%2C%20it%20still%20holds%20the%20status%20of%20a%20national%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal's%20obituary%20has%20been%20written%20often%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20every%20time%2C%20he%20has%20risen%20from%20the%20ashes%20like%20a%20phoenix.%20The%20latest%20crisis%20is%20unlike%20any%20other%20though.%20It%20is%20existential.%20It%20will%20take%20deeper%20introspection%20and%20great%20courage%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20old%20drawing%20board%20if%20the%20AAP%20and%20its%20boss%20are%20serious%20about%20regaining%20the%20confidence%20of%20those%20who%20sided%20with%20him%20for%2010%20long%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EAshutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0SatyaHindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739022900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F76ki14e_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_15_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi-polls-and-aap-rout-is-this-a-setback-or-a-wipeout-only-kejriwal-can-decide-7663263%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kejriwals%20obituary%20has%20been%20written%20often%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20every%20time%2C%20he%20has%20risen%20from%20the%20ashes%20like%20a%20phoenix.%20The%20latest%20crisis%20is%20unlike%20any%20other%20though.%20It%20is%20existential.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdelhi