ng%20submerged%20in%20water%20well.%20The%20flashlight%20also%20withstood%20a%2010-foot%20drop%20without%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20brightness%20tests%2C%20the%20TC15%20did%20an%20extraordinary%20job.%20It%20barely%20missed%20out%20on%20being%20the%20brightest%20from%20the%20start%2C%20and%20it%20only%20dimmed%20slightly%20over%20the%20next%20hour%20and%20a%20half.%20It%20was%20the%20brightest%20by%20far%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20testing%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20brightness%20levels%20plus%20a%20strobe%20mode%20effect.%20Max%20brightness%20should%20only%20be%20used%20for%2010%20minutes%20at%20most%20to%20protect%20the%20battery%3B%20plus%2C%20I%20found%20the%20light%20gets%20too%20hot%20to%20hold%20if%20it's%20on%20Turbo%20for%20any%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20performed%20well%2C%20there%20were%20a%20few%20downsides%3A%20You%20need%20an%2018650%20battery%20to%20operate%20the%20flashlight%2C%20but%20it%20comes%20with%20one%20rechargeable%20battery%20and%20a%20micro%20USB%20charge%20cord.%20Since%20the%20light%20runs%20so%20bright%2C%20the%20battery%20lasted%20less%20than%20two%20hours%20on%20top%20mode.%20You%20likely%20won't%20use%20that%20high%20for%20long%2C%20and%20the%20dimmer%20modes%20lasted%20much%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20on%2Foff%2Fmode%20button%20is%20also%20very%20easy%20to%20accidentally%20turn%20on.%20Switching%20between%20modes%20isn't%20intuitive%2C%20either%2C%20requiring%20you%20to%20double-click%20to%20access%20different%20modes.%20You%20might%20need%20to%20keep%20the%20user%20manual%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f34efbd7-679a-4b16-97ea-c854ed33978e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dorcy%20Floating%20Flashlight%20is%20full%20of%20features%20that%20make%20it%20ideal%20for%20outdoor%20use%20%E2%80%94%20boating%2C%20camping%2C%20hiking%20%E2%80%94%20and%20costs%20less%20than%20%2410.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20on