nch%20aluminum%20torch%20outshines%20most%20competitors.%20While%20the%20mode-switching%20interface%20takes%20some%20getting%20used%20to%2C%20the%20LC90's%20robust%20construction%20proved%20its%20worth%20in%20our%20drop%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Li-ion%20battery%20offers%20reliable%20power%20with%20convenient%20USB%20charging%2C%20providing%20four%20hours%20of%20runtime%20on%20high%20and%20six%20hours%20on%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20slightly%20heavier%20at%20eight%20ounces%20and%20having%20IP65%20water%20resistance%20(suitable%20for%20rain%20but%20not%20submersion)%2C%20the%20LC90%20balances%20functionality%20and%20durability.%20Three%20brightness%20levels%20plus%20emergency%20modes%20supply%20versatility%20for%20various%20situations%2C%20from%20power%20outages%20to%20outdoor%20adventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20distinguishes%20the%20LC90%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20maintain%20impressive%20brightness%20after%20the%20initial%20output%20settles.%20While%20we%20observed%20some%20dimming%20within%20the%20first%2010%20minutes%2C%20it%20maintained%20a%20strong%2C%20consistent%20beam%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20our%2090-minute%20test%20period%2C%20outperforming%20most%20flashlights%20in%20sustained%20brightness.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223abbbb8c-b215-44ea-ae54-132581436d7f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20small%5C%22%3EBest%20small%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20penlights%20don't%20light%20up%20a%20very%20big%20area%2C%20if%20you%20need%20bright%20beam%20directed%20in%20one%20specific%20place%2C%20and%20need%20quick-access%20to%20that%20light%2C%20the%20Coast%20HP3R%20Penlight%20does%20an%20excellent%20job.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoast%20focuses%20on%20LED%20lights%20for%20professionals%20such%20as%20law%20enforcement%2C%20search%20and%20rescue%20teams%2C%20and%20oil%20rig%20workers.%20Jake%20Keller%2C%20the%20SAR%20trainer%20we%20interviewed%20for%20this%20article%2C%20lists%20Coast%20as%20one%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20brands%20he%20highly%20recommends.%20And%2C%20the%20company%20backs%20its%20products%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fredirect.viglink.com%2F%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcoastportland.com%252Fpages%252Fwarranty%26key%3Da0a489b80c119e1fb25b8b4606294f7e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lifetime%20warranty%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20defects%20in%20workmanship%20and%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HP3R%20Penlight%20is%20small%20enough%20to%20pop%20into%20your%20shirt%20or%20pants%20pocket.%20I%20liked%20that%20it%20can%20operate%20on%20the%20included%202%20AAA%20alkaline%20batteries%20or%20included%20Li-ion%20rechargeable%20battery%2C%20which%20charges%20with%20an%20included%2C%20standard%20micro%20USB%20charging%20cord.%20The%20alkaline%20batteries%20lasted%20much%20longer%20(72%2B%20hours%20vs.%206%20hours%20on%20high)%2C%20but%20the%20rechargeable%20batteries%20produced%20a%20brighter%20beam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20power%20source%20was%20particularly%20bright%20compared%20to%20the%20full-size%20flashlights%2C%20but%20thanks%20to%20the%20adjustable%20lens%2C%20you%20can%20direct%20the%20beam%20right%20where%20you%20want%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20beam%20distance%20is%20up%20to%2093%20meters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20light%20is%20IPX4%20water-resistant%2C%20so%20it's%20protected%20from%20splashes%20of%20water%20but%20can't%20handle%20submersion.%20The%20aluminum%20body%20handled%20the%20drop%20test%20with%20no%20effects%20on%20its%20performance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20downsides%20are%20the%20penlight%20is%20easy%20to%20accidentally%20turn%20on%2C%20and%20it%20takes%20some%20practice%20to%20get%20the%20hang%20of%20adjusting%20between%20its%20two%20brightness%20options.%20It%20does%20remember%20the%20last%20mode%20you%20were%20on%2C%20which%20is%20nice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d0563ac4-29ce-402e-8568-d211d4b38207%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20EDC%5C%22%3EBest%20EDC%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20my%20extensive%20hands-on%20testing%2C%20the%20ThruNite%20Archer%202A%20is%20the%20best%20EDC%20flashlight%20(every%20day%20carry)%20because%20it%20masterfully%20balances%20durability%2C%20user-friendly%20design%2C%20and%20versatility.%20This%20pocket-friendly%20powerhouse%20measures%20just%206%20inches%20long%20and%20weighs%20a%20mere%203.56%20ounces%20with%20batteries%2C%20yet%20exceeds%20expectations%20with%20its%20outstanding%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Archer%202A%20features%20four%20brightness%20modes%20plus%20a%20strobe.%20Its%20intuitive%20controls%20prevent%20accidental%20activation%20while%20remaining%20easily%20accessible%20even%20with%20gloves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20aircraft-grade%20anodized%20aluminum%20construction%20proved%20remarkably%20resilient%20in%20my%20testing%2C%20surviving%2010-foot%20drops%20without%20missing%20a%20beat%20%E2%80%94%20the%20light%20continued%20functioning%20flawlessly.%20The%20IPX8%20waterproof%20rating%20isn't%20just%20marketing%20speak%3B%20our%20submersion%20test%20confirmed%20the%20Archer%202A's%20ability%20to%20run%20reliably%20underwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20initial%20brightness%20impressed%20me%2C%20I%20observed%20some%20dimming%20after%2030%20minutes%20on%20high%20power.%20Yet%2C%20this%20trade-off%20enables%20impressive%20runtime%20specs%3A%20six%20hours%20on%20high%20beam%20and%20up%20to%2028%20days%20on%20low.%20The%20convenience%20of%20standard%20AA%20batteries%20makes%20this%20light%20especially%20practical%20for%20everyday%20carry%20and%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20truly%20sets%20the%20Archer%202A%20apart%20is%20its%20combination%20of%20professional-grade%20features%20in%20a%20practical%20form%20factor%20for%20daily%20use.%20It%20can%20deliver%20reliable%20illumination%2C%20whether%20clipped%20to%20a%20pocket%20or%20stashed%20in%20a%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22083a6364-2af6-46d8-a36a-f5e3ca6d59bb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20flashlight%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20holds%20a%20flashlight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a67e986630eb10385c016a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20looked%20closely%20to%20each%20flashlight's%20brightness%2C%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20and%20size%2C%20but%20also%20consider%20diverse%20needs%20like%20battery%20type%20and%20adjustable%20focus%20abilities.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20choosing%20a%20flashlight%2C%20there%20are%20a%20number%20of%20factors%20Jake%20Keller%2C%20head%20training%20advisor%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fmcsosar.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMultnomah%20County%20(Oregon)%20Sheriff's%20Office%20Search%20%26amp%3B%20Rescue%20Team%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%20recommended%20considering%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20an%20everyday%20carry%20application%2C%20I%20look%20for%20something%20small%20that%20easily%20fits%20into%20a%20pocket.%20I'd%20sacrifice%20an%20adjustable%20focus%20and%20battery%20life%20in%20favor%20of%20something%20small%2C%20bright%2C%20and%20quick%20to%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20tests%2C%20I%20paid%20special%20attention%20to%20brightness%2C%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20and%20size%2C%20but%20since%20different%20users%20have%20diverse%20needs%2C%20I%20also%20looked%20at%20battery%20runtime%20and%20adjustable%20focus%20abilities.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you're%20on%20a%20hiking%20trip%2C%20you%20may%20not%20have%20easy%20access%20to%20a%20charging%20port%20and%20may%20not%20want%20the%20added%20weight%20of%20extra%20batteries.%20This%20is%20where%20a%20longer%20battery%20runtime%20comes%20in%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea773ed5-f00d-4734-b023-84b19ad0b8bd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20flashlights%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20checks%20the%20lumens%20of%20a%20flashlight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a67e987bb3f854015c4363%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20used%20a%20light%20meter%20to%20measure%20the%20lumens%20of%20each%20flashlight%20to%20assess%20brightness.%20%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20tests%20I%20put%20each%20model%20through%20to%20thoroughly%20review%20each%20option.%20The%20most%20important%20factors%20to%20consider%20are%20brightness%2C%C2%A0battery%20power%2C%20light%20modes%2C%C2%A0and%C2%A0durability.%20Here's%20how%20I%20considered%20each%20of%20those%20factors%20while%20testing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrightness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20used%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_101617_best-flashlights-20%26h%3D66af0fea6b782e4779ad5939451debc74b98ce5504636c42e843010661c860b0%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f416b0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-flashlight%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB005A0ETXY%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elight%20meter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20old%20mattress%20box%20to%20measure%20the%20lumens%20of%20each%20flashlight.%20I%20cut%20two%20holes%20in%20one%20end%20of%20the%2042-inch-long%20box%20(one%20hole%20for%20the%20flashlight%20to%20shine%20through%20and%20another%20for%20the%20light%20sensor).%20I%20then%20covered%20the%20interior%20with%20white%20paper%20and%20measured%20the%20lumens%20of%20the%20reflected%20light%20with%20the%20flashlight%20set%20to%20max%20brightness%20and%20a%20wide%20beam.%20I%20recorded%20measurements%20every%2010%20minutes%20for%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half.%20This%20showed%20both%20the%20brightness%20of%20the%20reflected%20light%20and%20how%20that%20changed%20over%20time.%20For%20most%20models%2C%20the%20lumen%20output%20decreased%20by%20at%20least%2050%20percent%20in%20the%20first%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20power%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20the%2090-minute%20brightness%20test%2C%20I%20let%20each%20battery%20operate%20on%20high%20until%20it%20was%20out%20of%20juice.%20Though%20a%20few%20still%20produced%20a%20dim%20light%20after%20a%20few%20hours%20some%20put%20off%20a%20marginally%20bright%20light%20for%20days.%20I%20also%20looked%20at%20whether%20the%20flashlight%20used%20common%20batteries%20(i.e.%2C%20AA%20or%20AAA)%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20replace%20or%20if%20it%20used%20a%20popular%20charging%20cord%20in%20the%20case%20of%20rechargeable%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELight%20modes%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHow%20many%20brightness%20options%20are%20there%3F%20Are%20there%20other%20colors%20or%20functions%2C%20such%20as%20strobe%20or%20SOS%3F%20Is%20it%20easy%20to%20switch%20between%20the%20different%20modes%3F%20These%20are%20all%20questions%20I%20considered%20when%20examining%20each%20flashlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20You%20don't%20want%20your%20flashlight%20to%20break%20easily.%20To%20test%20durability%2C%20I%20dropped%20each%20flashlight%20from%2010%20feet%20above%20a%20flight%20of%20hardwood%20stairs.%20None%20of%20the%20flashlights%20broke%20but%20the%20light%20went%20out%20on%20a%20few%20of%20them%2C%20which%20would%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20find%20if%20dropped%20in%20the%20dark.%20I%20also%20looked%20at%20whether%20they%20were%20waterproof%20or%20just%20water-resistant.%20If%20waterproof%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIP_Code%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIPX8%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20I%20submerged%20the%20flashlight%20in%20water%20for%20at%20least%20five%20minutes%20to%20see%20if%20it%20continued%20to%20function%20normally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20I%20examined%20whether%20the%20flashlights%20had%20adjustable%20focus%2C%20were%20easy%20to%20turn%20on%20by%20accident%2C%20and%20how%20they%20were%20to%20operate%20with%20gloves%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7be3ddf-2f74-479f-a751-ec1aee79b299%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EFlashlight%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-test%3D%5C%22faq-question-field%5C%22%3EDo%20LED%20flashlights%20get%20hot%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELED%20flashlights%20can%20generate%20significant%20heat%2C%20especially%20in%20high-output%20modes.%20While%20LEDs%20are%20more%20efficient%20than%20traditional%20incandescent%20bulbs%2C%20they%20still%20require%20thermal%20management.%20High-performance%20LED%20flashlights%20usually%20incorporate%20aluminum%20heat%20sinks%20and%20thermal%20protection%20circuits%20to%20avoid%20overheating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-test%3D%5C%22faq-question-field%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20an%20%26quot%3BEDC%20flashlight%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20EDC%20(everyday%20carry)%20flashlight%20is%20a%20reliable%2C%20compact%20light%20designed%20for%20convenient%20pocket%20carry%20and%20daily%20use.%20These%20lights%20feature%20multiple%20brightness%20modes%2C%20efficient%20LED%20emitters%2C%20and%20heavy-duty%20aluminum%20construction.%20The%20best%20EDC%20flashlights%20combine%20output%2C%20runtime%2C%20and%20size%20to%20serve%20emergencies%20and%20routine%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-test%3D%5C%22faq-question-field%5C%22%3EHow%20many%20lumens%20do%20you%20need%20in%20a%20flashlight%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20flashlight%20brightness%20depends%20on%20your%20needs.%2020%20to%20150%20lumens%20is%20enough%20for%20everyday%20indoor%20tasks.%20Most%20outdoor%20activities%20benefit%20from%20200%20to%20500%20lumens%2C%20while%20tactical%20or%20search%20and%20rescue%20applications%20may%20need%20over%201000%20lumens.%20Consider%20that%20higher%20lumens%20often%20trade%20runtime%20for%20brightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Wowtac%20A7%20Tactical%20Flashlight%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wowtac%20flashlight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f2c5e412438173f5775c23e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EVery%20bright%2C%20five%20brightness%20modes%20plus%20strobe%2C%20IPX8%20waterproof%20rating%2C%20long-lasting%20rechargeable%20Li-ion%20battery%2C%20fits%20easily%20into%20a%20pocket%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUses%20an%20uncommon%2018650%20battery%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wowtac%20A7%20Tactical%20Flashlight%20was%20the%20clear%20winner%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-flashlight%23how-we-test-flashlights-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20tests%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20When%20fully%20charged%2C%20the%20light%20was%20the%20brightest%20of%20all%20of%20the%20flashlights%20we%20tested%2C%20even%20after%2090%20minutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20A7%20has%20five%20brightness%20modes%20including%20a%20dim%20Firefly%20(at%20a%20reported%200.5%20lumens)%20and%20a%20battery%20runtime%20of%20108%20days.%20Turbo%20is%20the%20brightest%20and%20is%20meant%20for%20short%20periods%20of%20ultra-brightness%20%E2%80%94%20in%20our%20test%2C%20the%20lumens%20did%20drop%20dramatically%20after%2010%20minutes%20on%20this%20mode%2C%20so%20emphasis%20on%20%26quot%3Bshort%20periods%26quot%3B.%20There's%20also%20a%20Strobe%20mode%2C%20which%20has%20a%20high%20lumen%20output%20and%20is%20ideal%20for%20an%20emergency%20situation%20while%20camping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mode%20switching%20button%20is%20separate%20from%20the%20on%2Foff%20button%20which%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20keep%20the%20light%20set%20to%20your%20favorite%20and%20not%20have%20to%20cycle%20through%20every%20mode%20each%20time%20you%20turn%20it%20on.%20The%20torch%20overall%20is%20small%20(4.5%20inches)%20and%20easy%20to%20stow%2C%20and%20the%20on%2Foff%20button%20is%20raised%2C%20lowering%20the%20chances%20you'll%20accidentally%20turn%20it%20unit%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20durability%20test%2C%20the%20light%20did%20go%20out%20when%20it%20hit%20the%20ground%2C%20but%20it%20started%20working%20again%20once%20I%20picked%20it%20up.%20The%20flashlight%20also%20has%20an%20IPX8%20waterproof%20rating%2C%20which%20proved%20accurate%20as%20it%20handled%20full%20submersion%20without%20any%20impact%20on%20its%20performance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20downside%20is%20that%20this%20flashlight%20uses%20a%20less-common%20battery%2C%20a%2018650.%20However%2C%20the%20rechargeable%20battery%20that%20it%20comes%20with%20%3Cem%3Edoes%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Elast%2010%20hours%20on%20top%20brightness%2C%20and%20you%20can%20charge%20the%20light%20with%20the%20included%20micro%20USB%20cord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3A%20Dorcy%20Floating%20Flashlight%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dorcy%20flashlight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fa08a9e1df1d5001821875b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAffordable%2C%20easy-to-use%2C%20floats%2C%20waterproof%2C%20built-in%20carabiner%2C%20long-lasting%20battery%20with%20consistent%20brightness%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOnly%20one%20brightness%20mode%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dorcy%20Floating%20Flashlight%20is%20full%20of%20features%20that%20make%20it%20ideal%20for%20outdoor%20use%20%E2%80%94%20boating%2C%20camping%2C%20hiking%20%E2%80%94%20and%20costs%20less%20than%20%2410.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20only%20