0of%20the%20testing%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20brightness%20levels%20plus%20a%20strobe%20mode%20effect.%20Max%20brightness%20should%20only%20be%20used%20for%2010%20minutes%20at%20most%20to%20protect%20the%20battery%3B%20plus%20I%20found%20the%20light%20gets%20too%20hot%20to%20hold%20if%20it's%20on%20Turbo%20for%20any%20longer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it%20performed%20well%2C%20there%20were%20a%20few%20downsides%3A%20You%20need%20a%2018650%20battery%20to%20operate%20the%20flashlight%2C%20though%20it%20does%20come%20with%20one%20rechargeable%20battery%20and%20a%20micro%20USB%20charge%20cord.%20Since%20the%20light%20runs%20so%20bright%2C%20the%20battery%20lasted%20less%20than%20two%20hours%20on%20top%20mode.%20You%20likely%20won't%20use%20that%20high%20for%20long%2C%20and%20the%20dimmer%20modes%20lasted%20much%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20on%2Foff%2Fmode%20button%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20accidentally%20turn%20on.%20Switching%20between%20modes%20isn't%20intuitive%2C%20either%2C%20requiring%20you%20to%20double%20click%20to%20reach%20different%20modes.%20You'll%20might%20need%20to%20keep%20the%20user%20manual%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20penlight%3A%20Coast%20HP3R%20Penlight%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Coast%20HP3R%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f2c44d60ef1883b9a70654c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDual%20power%20with%202%20AAA%20batteries%20and%20rechargeable%20Li-ion%2C%20long%20battery%20life%2C%20adjustable%20beam%20focus%2C%20passed%20our%20drop%20test%2C%20doesn't%20roll%20easily%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELimited%20lighting%20modes%2C%20only%20IPX4%20water-resistant%2C%20easy%20to%20accidentally%20turn%20on%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20penlights%20don't%20light%20up%20a%2