o%20just%20LGB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20pages%20have%20also%20gone%20missing.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Army%20and%20Navy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fdaily-news%2F2025%2F02%2F06%2Farmy-navy-pull-down-web-pages-devoted-women-military-service.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremoved%3C%2Fa%3E%20webpages%20showcasing%20the%20contributions%20of%20female%20service%20members%20this%20week.%20Some%20of%20the%20pages%20were%20apparently%20restored%20after%20inquiries%20about%20the%20scrubbing%2C%20Military.com%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERet.%20Navy%20Adm.%20James%20Stavridis%2C%20the%20former%20top%20commander%20in%20Europe%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fstavridisj%2Fstatus%2F1887887631062589825%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20views%20of%20women%20in%20DoD%20today%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20mistake%26quot%3B%20with%20long-term%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20DoD%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bwill%20fully%20execute%20and%20implement%20all%20directives%20outlined%20in%20the%20Executive%20Orders%20issued%20by%20the%20President%2C%20ensuring%20that%20they%20are%20carried%20out%20with%20utmost%20professionalism%2C%20efficiency%2C%20and%20in%20alignment%20with%20national%20security%20objectives.%20We%20will%20provide%20status%20updates%20as%20we%20are%20able.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20provided%20a%20similar%20statement%20on%20its%20online%20activities%2C%20and%20the%20Navy%20told%20BI%20its%20stance%20was%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Pentagon's.%20The%20Marine%20Corps%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20Public%20Web%20had%20completed%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20review%20of%20public-facing%20content%20hosted%20across%20the%20Marines.mil%20enterprise.%26quot%3B%20The%20Coast%20Guard%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContent%20such%20as%20official%20messages%20and%20publications%20were%20not%20removed%2C%20instead%20requiring%20only%20a%20cancellation%20or%20revision.%20Historical%20and%20news-related%20content%20and%20videos%20weren't%20scrubbed%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuestions%20remain%20on%20who's%20been%20in%20charge%20of%20scrubbing%20the%20sites%3B%20the%20OPM%20memo%20appears%20to%20leave%20the%20task%20up%20to%20each%20individual%20agency.%20OPM%20also%20requested%20a%20complete%20list%20of%20actions%20taken%20by%20every%20department%20and%20any%20other%20plans%20to%20%26quot%3Bfully%20comply%20with%20this%20guidance%26quot%3B%20by%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pentagon%20also%20issued%20guidance%20last%20Friday%20from%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%20Pete%20Hegseth%20indicating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FReleases%2FRelease%2FArticle%2F4050331%2Fidentity-months-dead-at-dod%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentity%20months%20were%20%26quot%3Bdead%20at%20DoD%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20That%20included%20February's%20Black%20History%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20move%20comes%20amid%20new%20reports%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpost%2Fpreview%3Fsvapi%26post_id%3D679cecfbe72cf8b4936671bd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransgender%20service%20members%20are%20already%20being%20affected%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20and%20that%20identity-based%20clubs%20at%20West%20Point%20are%20being%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20developments%20have%20sparked%20concern%20among%20some%20advocacy%20groups.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20purges%20of%20DEI-related%20information%20from%20military%20websites%20and%20the%20targeting%20of%20specific%20communities%20in%20executive%20orders%20represent%20a%20significant%20step%20backward%20for%20inclusivity%20and%20equality%20within%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Cspan%3ERachel%20Branaman%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3EModern%20Military%20Association%20of%20America%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20moves%20signal%20%26quot%3Bthat%20certain%20individuals%20are%20not%20valued%20or%20welcome%20within%20the%20military%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20actions%20could%20have%20%26quot%3Bfar-reaching%20ramifications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20it's%20unclear%20if%20DoD's%20defense%20video%20and%20imagery%20distribution%20systems%2C%20known%20as%20DVIDS%2C%20will%20be%20updated.%20Defense%20Media%20Activity%20didn't%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20it%20still%20includes%20previous%20imagery%20and%20graphics%20celebrating%20identity%20months%20like%20Pride%20Month.%20Just%20last%20week%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20posted%20a%20graphic%20honoring%20Black%20History%20Month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245fdec10-707c-4740-a6ab-7d4425b1c3da%5C%22%3EThe%20State%20Department%2C%20CDC%2C%20and%20other%20sites%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20seen%20in%20a%20close%20up%20as%20he%20answers%20a%20question.%20His%20suit%20is%20dark%20blue%20and%20his%20tie%20is%20bright%20blue.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3bb687bb3f854015bded0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20executive%20order's%20effects%20on%20CDC%20databases%20and%20websites%20prompted%20massive%20backlash.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20federal%20government%20websites%2C%20such%20as%20those%20for%20the%20Department%20of%20State%2C%20were%20also%20scrubbed%20in%20line%20with%20Trump's%20executive%20order.%20This%20included%20the%20state%20department's%20travel%20guidance%20and%20resources%20for%20LGBTQ%2B%20people%2C%20which%20has%20also%20been%20stripped%20to%20just%20LGB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20unrelated%20content%2C%20such%20as%20cou