reement%20ruled%20out%20this%20possibility.%20Also%2C%20the%20AAP-Congress%20alliance%20during%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20did%20not%20yield%20good%20results%20for%20the%20Opposition%20and%20BJP%20won%20all%20seven%20Delhi%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20AAP%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20speaking%20in%20the%20same%20language%20as%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20it%20was%20not%20its%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20AAP's%20win.%20It%20must%2C%20however%2C%20be%20kept%20in%20mind%20that%20even%20with%20the%2011%20seats%20AAP%20lost%20to%20a%20split%20in%20Opposition%20votes%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20would%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark.%20So%20while%20the%20Congress%20candidates%20hurt%20AAP's%20prospects%2C%20the%20BJP%20clearly%20outperformed%20it%20in%20the%20capital%20fight.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20looks%20at%2011%20key%20seats%20where%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%20by%20slim%20margins%20while%20the%20Congress%20cornered%20a%20significant%20chunk%20of%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAAP's%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Parvesh%20Verma%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20constituency.%20The%20margin%20was%204%2C089%20votes.%20Congress's%20Sandeep%20Dikshit%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Sheila%20Dikshit's%20son%2C%20got%204%2C568%20votes%20and%20finished%20a%20distant%20third.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20had%20contested%20this%20election%20together%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20would%20have%20likely%20scored%20a%20slim%20victory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJangpura%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFormer%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20Number%202%20Manish%20Sisodia%20lost%20to%20BJP's%20Tarvinder%20Singh%20Marwah%20by%20a%20thin%20margin%20of%20675%20votes.%20Look%20at%20the%20candidate%20list%20and%20you%20find%20Congress's%20Farhad%20Suri%2C%20who%20got%207%2C350%20votes.%20An%20alliance%20would%20have%20likely%20transferred%20these%20votes%20to%20Mr%20Sisodia%20and%20ensured%20his%20comfortable%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGreater%20Kailash%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGreater%20Kailash%20in%20south%20Delhi%20was%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20safe%20seat%20for%20the%20AAP%20and%20many%20had%20hoped%20three-time%20MLA%20and%20minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20would%20win%20comfortably.%20But%20the%20BJP's%20Shikha%20Roy%20defeated%20Mr%20Bharadwaj%20by%20a%20margin%20of%203%2C188%20votes.%20The%20Congress's%20Garvit%20Singhvi%20won%206%2C711%20votes%20and%20if%20there%20was%20an%20alliance%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20Mr%20Bharadwaj%20won%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMalviya%20Nagar%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20similar%20story%20unfolded%20in%20Malviya%20Nagar%2C%20where%20BJP's%20Satish%20Upadhyay%20defeated%20three-time%20MLA%20Somnath%20Bharti%20by%20a%20margin%20of%202%2C131%20votes.%20The%20Congress's%20Jitender%20Kumar%20Kochar%20got%206%2C770%20votes%2C%20effectively%20ruining%20the%20game%20for%20the%20AAP%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBadli%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20Badli%2C%20BJP's%20Aahir%20Deepal%20Chaudharyy%20defeated%20AAP's%20Ajesh%20Yadav%20by%2015%2C163%20votes.%20The%20Congress%20Devender%20Yadav%20won%2041%2C071%20votes.%20If%20there%20had%20been%20an%20alliance%2C%20AAP%20could%20have%20had%20a%20smooth%20sail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimarpur%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBJP's%20Surya%20Prakash%20Khatri%20won%20Timarpur%20by%20a%20slim%20margin%20of%201%2C168%20votes%2C%20defeating%20the%20BJP's%20Surinder%20Pal%20Singh.%20The%20Congress%20Lokendra%20Kalyan%20Singh%20won%208%2C361%20votes%20and%20this%20worked%20to%20the%20BJP's%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENangloi%20Jat%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20BJP's%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Shokeen%20won%20the%20seat%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2026%2C251%20votes%2C%20defeating%20the%20AAP's%20Raghuvinder%20Shokeen.%20The%20Congress's%20Rohit%20Choudhary%20got%2032%2C028%20votes%20and%20ate%20into%20the%20Opposition%20votes%20that%20would%20have%20otherwise%20gone%20to%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERajinder%20Nagar%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESenior%20AAP%20leader%20Durgesh%20Pathak%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Umang%20Bajaj%20by%20a%20margin%20of%201%2C231%20votes.%20Vineet%20Yadav%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20who%20got%204%2C105%20votes%2C%20worked%20to%20the%20AAP's%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChhatarpur%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20south%20Delhi's%20Chhatarpur%2C%20BJP's%20Kartar%20Singh%20Tanwar%20defeated%20the%20AAP's%20Brahm%20Singh%20Tanwar%20by%20a%20margin%20of%206%2C239%20votes.%20The%20Congres's%20Rajender%20Singh%20Tanwar%20got%206%2C601%20votes%2C%20more%20than%20the%20margin%20of%20defeat.%20This%20worked%20to%20the%20BJP's%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESangam%20Vihar%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBJP's%20Chandan%20Kumar%20Choudhary%20won%20the%20election%20by%20the%20thinnest%20margin%20across%20the%20capital%2C%20defeating%20AAP's%20Dinesh%20Mohaniya%20by%20just%20344%20votes.%20In%20the%20same%20seat%2C%20Congress's%20Harsh%20Choudhary%20got%2015%2C863%20votes%20and%20spoiled%20the%20AAP's%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrilokpuri%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20east%20Delhi%20seat%20saw%20BJP's%20Ravi%20Kant%20winning%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20just%20392%20seats.%20AAP's%20Anjana%20Parcha%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress's%20Amardeep%2C%20who%20won%206%2C147%20votes%2C%20clearly%20split%20the%20Opposition%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739019480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvu8dmsjo_arvind-kejriwal-rahul-gandhi-rahul-kejriwal-650_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-results-2025-did-congress-hurt-aap-in-delhi-11-seats-tell-a-tale-7664856%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20BJP%20scored%20a%20massive%20win%20in