tionship%20with%20the%20man%20who%20became%20my%20husband%20and%20discovered%20he'd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-lived-apart-for-10-years-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20been%20married%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20had%20a%20child%2C%20I%20wanted%20the%20dynamic%20to%20be%20a%20very%20different%20experience%20for%20his%20son%2C%20who's%20now%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20really%20shifted%20gears%20when%20my%20husband's%20first%20wife%20went%20on%20to%20have%20two%20more%20sons%20with%20her%20new%20husband.%20I%20wanted%20my%20stepson%20to%20have%20the%20best%20relationship%20with%20his%20half-brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbe0cf08-e64c-4b46-a511-8c19695ae9af%5C%22%3EWe'd%20all%20spent%20time%20together%20before%20our%20trip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-vacationed-bali-18-family-members-a-disaster-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBali%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20had%20tested%20the%20waters%20and%20gotten%20together.%20Six%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20had%20invited%20everyone%20over%20to%20my%20house%20for%20a%20big%20Easter%20dinner.%20They%20stayed%20the%20night%20so%20the%20boys%20could%20all%20wake%20up%20together%20for%20Easter%20day%2C%20and%20my%20stepson%20could%20wake%20up%20with%20all%20his%20parents%20under%20one%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20went%20so%20well%20that%20when%20I%20found%20out%20I%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Bali%20to%20shoot%20some%20content%20for%20my%20job%20%E2%80%94%20I%20work%20in%20travel%20%E2%80%94%20I%20asked%20them%20all%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20come.%20I%20actually%20booked%20the%20tickets%20before%20anyone%20could%20back%20out!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESociety%20has%20rigid%20rules%20for%20how%20you%20should%20behave%20with%20your%20ex-spouse%2C%20especially%20women.%20It%20pits%20us%20against%20each%20other%3B%20I%20feel%20as%20though%20we're%20supposed%20to%20hate%20or%2C%20at%20the%20least%2C%20avoid%20each%20other%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstepmom-experience-didnt-want-kids-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erole%20of%20a%20stepmom%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20often%20demonized.%20I%20think%20people%20thought%20we%20were%20nuts%20because%20traveling%20together%20challenged%20those%20narratives%20they've%20absorbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20at%20that%20first%20Easter%20dinner%2C%20there%20were%20many%20awkward%20silences.%20I%20definitely%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20glasses%20of%20wine%20before%20they%20came%20over!%20I%20was%20very%20aware%20that%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20blended%20families%2C%20there%20can%20be%20head-butting%20over%20roles%20and%20territorial%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20remember%20worrying%20about%20whether%20there'd%20be%20lingering%20looks%20or%20remaining%20chemistry.%20It%20was%20paranoia%20%E2%80%94%20I%20now%20know%20I%20needn't%20have%20worried.%20You%20have%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20on%20yourself%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flessons-learned-breakups-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20past%20your%20last%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20trust%20in%20your%20new%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20worked%20for%20us%20was%20always%20coming%20back%20to%20what%20truly%20matters%3A%20the%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20kids.%20When%20we%20collaborate%2C%20they%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231bfc757-ad70-4d96-8771-c5fa1e487a6b%5C%22%3EThe%20vacation%20strengthened%20our%20bonds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Bali%20vacation%2C%20we%20adults%20thrived%20too.%20I%20can%20honestly%20say%20it%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultigenerational-family-vacation-tips-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeasiest%20group%20holiday%3C%2Fa%3E%20I've%20ever%20been%20on.%20We'd%20tag-team%20babysitting%20duties%20so%20couples%20could%20have%20date%20nights%20